# Monorepo boundaries

This repository contains **independent monorepos**. Do not merge them.

| Path | Role | Package manager |
|------|------|-----------------|
| `next-forge/` | Apps, Mintlify docs, Storybook workshop | Bun |
| `GenerativeUI_monorepo/` | Legacy agent stack (CopilotKit, agent-server) | Yarn 3.3 |
| `GenerativeUI_monorepo/UniversalWorkbench*/` | Separate product (read-only unless tasked) | Yarn 4.10 |

## Allowed integration

- HTTP, WebSocket, or published npm packages between stacks.
- Shared documentation links (Mintlify → `docs/codebase/`).

## Forbidden

- `workspace:*` dependencies across `next-forge/` and `GenerativeUI_monorepo/`.
- Relative imports like `../../GenerativeUI_monorepo/...` from next-forge apps.
- Deleting or converting GenerativeUI lockfiles during next-forge work.
